{"tid":1708500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實人人都可以輕鬆塞鐵","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T00:54:10.000Z","uid":55932,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f0118b068265fbfac11334c2e0b28003784a18","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"兩三個人一組<br />\n著斯文返工衫<br />\n上到車企附近扮唔識<br />\n差唔多埋站搵一個暈低作嘔<br />\n另一個去㩒緊急制<br />\n記得要好認真好似識急救咁<br />\n叫大家散開俾空氣佢唔好亂郁佢<br />\n要等職員黎先慢慢抬佢出車箱<br />\n記得隊友要幫手一齊搬<br />\n廢事乘機俾藍絲抽水或者粗暴對待<br />\n狗鐵職員會問你咩唔舒服<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">女手足記得話黎m</span></strong><br />\n班狗鐵姨姨會突然好同情你斟暖水俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到月台職員會扶你去坐下<br />\n正常人血糖低都會全身冇力 反下白眼仆兩仆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐低等佢地拎杯水俾你<br />\n廢事班職員知道太多人玩野搞之後將扮唔舒服嘅手足夾硬抬出車快快手搞掂就算<br />\n做個禮貌寶寶講埋唔好意思唔該哂就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐多陣就可以搭多兩個站再暈過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知啦 係架車到咁多人焗咁耐頭暈係好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家見到有人唔舒服記得出手相助<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">專業嘔吐師唔好嘔係扶手位 會廢左佢半卡車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好再要手足冒險無啦啦走去拉緊急制 你坐一坐地下就俾到理由手足去做野 又唔驚俾其他乘客屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢屌你你就理直氣壯屌返佢有人唔舒服call車長有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過記得唔好濫用救護車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac470df7550f37752acab17f16ac0957a2ebb58d","tid":1708500,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"最好一人帶一個大喼返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 搬屋師/升降師<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704038</a>"},{"pid":"0af960c435f75a47282655f5361e2ec9625c7efb","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14d26eb6a04194719fb8e31f79feec136c62316","tid":1708500,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a606b8ad8c24ef15b8182d4edf5fe309bb7848","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e43eff80a126912de5789e7dd2da6e6a4e8dff","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"聽日黎場嘔吐袋收集大賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba79db7b176a955186ec248066023d3e2a4ef60","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"和理非做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n月經師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5d33981d0010453710b053ea4c024f9042ac1f","tid":1708500,"uid":136227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"香港有冇臭屁彈買？"},{"pid":"abc92f601c9bfb2f6792f12241c58863611bd79a","tid":1708500,"uid":55932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8f5d33981d0010453710b053ea4c024f9042ac1f","tid":1708500,"uid":136227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"香港有冇臭屁彈買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"一陣就散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=